5　　日\r\n\r\n                             書記官　陳  嬿  如","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KSBA/110%2c%e8%a8%b4%e6%9b%b4%e4%b8%80%2c11%2c20220225%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KSBA,110,訴更一,11,20220225,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"訴更一","JNO":"11","JDATE":"20220225","JTITLE":"廢棄物清理法"}